{"tid":2141780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平六四角色曝光 阻學生串聯","createTime":"2020-08-06T03:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T05:13:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"53871e3bbcd3b5ece1423f50058a240793d986e6","tid":2141780,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:13:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200806/LSPKT22C73COIWBYAB7ZVYKVEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200806%2FLSPKT22C73COIWBYAB7ZVYKVEY%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=424b553d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200806%2FLSPKT22C73COIWBYAB7ZVYKVEY%2F&h=7c10f692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200806/LSPKT22C73COIWBYAB7ZVYKVEY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n習近平六四角色曝光 阻學生串聯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2LSZmEgi8j9ywYW7MEemlOb8En0=/753x502/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V67SMEILSGVDZQKXHLSO7SK27E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2LSZmEgi8j9ywYW7MEemlOb8En0%3D%2F753x502%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV67SMEILSGVDZQKXHLSO7SK27E.gif&h=8bcf22c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北京街頭的戶外電視播放着習近平講話的片段。路透社<br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平當年在八九民運的角色罕有曝光。中共中央黨校主辦的《學習時報》披露，時任福建省寧德地委書記的習近平在1989年「妥善處置學潮風波」，包括阻截抗議學生從浙江進入福建串聯，「六四」後秋後算賬時「縮小打擊面」但又「不搞人人過關」等，似是吹捧習在關鍵時刻的指揮能力。<br />\n<br />\n新一期《學習時報》刊出。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黨校學報吹捧習事迹<br />\n<br />\n習獲悉後批示：「第一要認定中央、跟定中央，一切聽從黨中央指揮；第二要堅決阻止學生入閩串聯，汽車上的標語更不能進寧德、進福建。」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳由誠說，風波平息。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《學習時報》"},{"pid":"d78b5888b5b6769dad6c3a7be90adb69d97e3a93","tid":2141780,"uid":149494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:15:23.000Z","msg":"當年梁振英、建制派同香港藝人都支持學生，反對共產黨鎮壓<br />\n即係呢班人全部反過習近平"},{"pid":"f99cabc959ebd67462a4d51243d78a7dcfcd7bcb","tid":2141780,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"64又關你事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9e2fe6861fb2ba7add5bbaaf848a0f0cb2afe9","tid":2141780,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f99cabc959ebd67462a4d51243d78a7dcfcd7bcb","tid":2141780,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"64又關你事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"就嚟抗日都關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97946f733bb2aca88fb4ff4386ab04954b3aaf71","tid":2141780,"uid":309553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f99cabc959ebd67462a4d51243d78a7dcfcd7bcb","tid":2141780,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"64又關你事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:26:20.000Z","msg":"親自指揮"},{"pid":"3603f24432078989f990f2488e4b6f1536251662","tid":2141780,"uid":262093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"習近平出生時，天放異光，地動山搖"},{"pid":"7f1c48602bc8105a49d660888c01decc89a5e385","tid":2141780,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d78b5888b5b6769dad6c3a7be90adb69d97e3a93","tid":2141780,"uid":149494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:15:23.000Z","msg":"當年梁振英、建制派同香港藝人都支持學生，反對共產黨鎮壓<br />\n即係呢班人全部反過習近平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"咁你呢"},{"pid":"ca040fe22666524ad3977b510f2eacbbe17cc254","tid":2141780,"uid":155784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3603f24432078989f990f2488e4b6f1536251662","tid":2141780,"uid":262093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score